org.sql: SELECT journals.id AS event_id, journals.created_at AS event_datetime, journals.user_id AS event_author, journals.notes AS event_description, journals.version AS version, journals.journable_id AS journable_id, changeset_journals.revision AS revision, changeset_journals.comments AS comments, changeset_journals.committed_on AS committed_on, repositories.project_id AS project_id, repositories.type AS repository_type FROM journals INNER JOIN changeset_journals ON journals.data_id = changeset_journals.id AND journals.data_type = 'Journal::ChangesetJournal' INNER JOIN repositories ON changeset_journals.repository_id = repositories.id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = repositories.project_id WHERE journals.journable_type = 'Changeset' AND journals.user_id = 653 AND projects.id IN (SELECT enabled_modules.project_id FROM enabled_modules WHERE name = 'activity') AND projects.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT projects.id FROM projects INNER JOIN enabled_modules ON projects.id = enabled_modules.project_id AND enabled_modules.name IN ('repository') AND projects.active = True WHERE projects.active = True) ORDER BY journals.id DESC LIMIT 10
